  "description": "Shree Sagarmatha Vidhya Mandir is a renowned educational institution dedicated to nurturing young minds from early childhood through the secondary level (Grades 1–10). Situated in a serene and supportive environment, the school blends modern teaching methodologies with Nepal’s rich cultural values. With a team of qualified, caring educators, the school focuses on holistic development—academic excellence, moral integrity, creativity, and physical fitness. State-of-the-art classrooms, a well-stocked library, science and computer labs, and spacious playgrounds provide an ideal setting for learning. Regular co-curricular activities, including sports, arts, music, and public speaking, ensure students grow into confident, disciplined, and responsible citizens. At Shree Sagarmatha Vidhya Mandir, every child is guided to scale their own “Everest” of success.",
